Core technology

Five pillars of performance

Every UnityESS component is selected, tested, and integrated to work as a unified system — not assembled from catalog parts.

01

Unity EMS

In-house Energy Management System. Real-time monitoring across every cell, every cluster, every cycle. Predictive diagnostics. Automatic charge-discharge optimization. >99% system uptime.

02

LFP Chemistry

The safest lithium-ion chemistry available. 10,000+ cycle life. Zero thermal runaway risk. No cobalt, no nickel, no supply chain anxiety.

03

Liquid cooling

Cell-level thermal management. Temperature delta within ±2°C across the entire array. Consistent performance from Rajasthan's 48°C summers to Himalayan winters.

04

Fire suppression

Multi-layer defense. Aerosol at module level. Gas at container level. Off-gas detection with response under 10 seconds. Meets IEC 62619, UL 1973, UL 9540A.

05

DC-coupled architecture

Solar connects directly to the battery bus. No redundant DC-AC-DC conversion. Higher round-trip efficiency, lower BOS cost, smaller footprint.
